<p>
    <strong>Privacy Policy</strong><br/><br/>
    ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair respects the privacy of the personal information and your data and will ensure
    compliance by its staff to the strictest standards of security and confidentiality in respect of all personal
    information and data submitted by you via the Site and ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will not, subject to the
    terms herein, release such information to anyone without your prior consent (whether registered or not).<br/><br/>
    You are strongly recommended to read this privacy statement (“Privacy Statement”) carefully to have an understanding
    of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair policy and practices with regard to the treatment of personal information
    and data provided by Users on the Site. This Privacy Statement is applicable to both registered and unregistered
    Users, and the terms herein may be updated, revised, varied and/or amended from time to time as ICON Virtual
    Internship And Job Fair may deem necessary and/or appropriate.<br/><br/>
    By registering for or using the services/Site, or by clicking the ‘Sign up’ button, you:<br/><br/>
<ul>
    <li>Consent to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair’ group companies
        collecting, using, disclosing and/or processing your personal data for the purposes as described below;
    </li>
    <li>Consent to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair group companies
        disclosing your personal data to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or ICON Virtual Internship And Job
        Fair’ group companies’ third party service providers or agents (whether within or outside Singapore) for the
        purposes as described below.
    </li>
</ul>
If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Statement, please contact the Data Protection Officer, whose contact details are set out under the section headed “Enquiries” below.
<br/><br/>
In this Privacy Statement, the following terms shall have the respective meanings specified below unless the context otherwise requires:
<br/><br/>
<ul>
    <li>“Advertiser(s)” means a User or Company who places a job advertisement or promotes any job related activities
        via the Site.
    </li>
    <li>“ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair” means ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Intern Pte Ltd.</li>
    <li>“Job Seeker(s)” means users seeking employment.</li>
    <li>“Sign up User(s)” means Users who sign up on the Site to obtain services offered by ICON Virtual Internship And
        Job Fair. Unless the context provides otherwise, references in this Privacy Statement to “users” or “you”
        include references to generic users and Registered Users.
    </li>
    <li>“Site” means any website, job portal or mobile application owned and operated by ICON Virtual Internship And Job
        Fair and its affiliates/subsidiaries or its service providers.
    </li>
</ul>
<strong>Purpose of Collection and Use of Personal Data</strong><br/><br/>
In the course of using the Site, you may disclose or be asked to provide personal information and/or data. In order to have the benefit of and enjoy various services offered by the Site, it may be necessary for you to provide ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair with your personal information and/or data. Although you are not obliged to provide the information and/or data as requested on the Site, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will not be able to render certain services on the Site in the event that you fail to do so.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair purposes for collecting and using the information and data on the Site include but are not limited to the following:
<br/><br/>
<ul>
    <li>for the daily operation of the services provided to you;</li>
    <li>to assist you to find appropriate employment with Employers and to assist Employers to assess the suitability of
        candidates for a job vacancy for a wide spectrum of jobs and industries;
    </li>
    <li>to provide you with various services offered by the Site and newsletters, information on job openings and
        promotional and marketing materials (for further details, please refer to section headed “Subscription of
        Newsletter/Promotional Materials/Marketing Materials” below);
    </li>
    to handle and follow up on enquiries, requests and complaints from you;
    <li>to contact you regarding administrative notices and communications relevant to your use of the Site and to
        respond to your inquiries or requests;
    </li>
    <li>to assist ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair with developments for future marketing and promoting purposes or
        other internal purposes;
    </li>
    <li>to verify your identity in posted advertisements, materials, representations, messages, views or comments or
        such other information (collectively “Information“) on the Site;
    </li>
    <li>to identify who viewed the Information posted on the Site;</li>
    <li>to allow you to enjoy your benefits as members of the Site by enrolling for special events and promotions hosted
        by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or its affiliates and/or partner companies;
    </li>
    <li>to facilitate ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or its affiliates to use your personal data for the
        purposes relating to the provision of services offered by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and marketing
        services and/or special events of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or its affiliates;
    </li>
    <li>to obtain statistics to analyze usage of the Site in order to help its further development; and</li>
    <li>for purposes other than the above mentioned which are related to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and/or its
        affiliates’ provision of their product and/or services.
    </li>
</ul>
Before using the Site or disclosing any information or data on the Site, if you are a minor in the jurisdiction in which you reside, you should seek prior consent from a person with parental responsibility for you, e.g. parent or guardian, who may contact the responsible Data Protection Officer whose contact details are set out under the section headed “Enquiries”.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair strives to only collect personal data which are necessary and adequate but not excessive in relation to the purposes set out hereinabove.
<br/><br/>
If ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair requires the use of your personal data for a purpose other than those set out hereinabove, we will request your prescribed consent to the same. If you are a minor, the prescribed consent should be given by your parent or guardian.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Collection of Personal Data</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair may collect personal information and/or data about you, such as your name, login ID and password, address, email address, phone number, age, gender, date of birth, country of residence, nationality, education level and work experience that is/are not otherwise publicly available. Occasionally, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair may also collect additional personal information and/or data from you in connection with contests, surveys, or special offers.
<br/><br/>
Only duly authorized staff of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will be permitted to access your personal information and data, and ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair shall not release such personal information and data to any third parties save except in the circumstances listed under the section headed “Disclosure or Transfer of Data” below.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Disclosure or Transfer of Data</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair agrees to take all practicable steps to keep all personal information and data of Users confidential and/or undisclosed, subject to the following.
<br/><br/>
Generally speaking, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will only disclose and/or transfer your personal information and/or data to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair personnel and staff for the purpose of providing services to you and corporate clients of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair who have made specific requests for such information and/or data with your prior consent. However, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair may disclose and/or transfer such information and/or data to third parties under the following circumstances:
<br/><br/>
<ul>
    <li>where the information and/or data is disclosed and/or transferred to any third party suppliers or external
        service providers who have been duly authorized by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair to use such information
        and/or data and who will facilitate the services on the Site, under a duty of confidentiality;
    </li>
    <li>where the information and/or data is disclosed and/or transferred to any agents, affiliates or associates of
        ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair who have been duly authorized by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair to
        use such information and/or data;
    </li>
    <li>where permitted under the “Terms and Conditions” including the “Talent Search Terms and Conditions” (see the
        Profiles Section below);
    </li>
    <li>where ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair needs to protect and defend its rights and property;</li>
    <li>where ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair considers necessary to do so in order to comply with the applicable
        laws and regulations, including without limitation compliance with a judicial proceeding, court order, or legal
        process served on the Site;
    </li>
    <li>where ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair deems necessary in order to deliver the products and services that we
        offer and cultivate a positive user experience; and/or
    </li>
    <li>where ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair deems necessary in order to maintain and/or improve the services on
        the Site.
    </li>
</ul>
Personal data collected via the Site may be transferred, stored and processed in any country in which ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair or any member of the ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Group operates. By using the Site, you are deemed to have agreed to, consented to and authorized ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair to disclose and/or transfer your personal information and data under the circumstances stated above, as well as to any transfer of information (including the Information) outside of your country.
<br/><br/>
<strong>ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Advertisers and Online Applications</strong><br/><br/>
Making an online application to a job advertisement on the Site is a free and optional service that requires you to complete mandatory fields (for example first name, last name, phone and email) so that Advertisers can identify and contact the applicants. When you apply for a job advertisement on the Site, applications, including attachments and cover letters, are:
<br/><br/>
<ul>
    <li>forwarded directly on to the Advertiser and/or its nominated representative; and/or</li>
    <li>stored in the ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Employers Portal on behalf of the Advertiser.</li>
</ul>
The ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Employers Portal allows Advertisers to easily and effectively manage their recruitment process via one central facility made available by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair.
<br/><br/>
By applying to a position advertised on the Site you are requesting that ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair pass the information you provide to the relevant Advertiser and/or their nominated representative. Any questions you have relating to a position advertised on ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair, your online application and/or the status of your application should be directed directly to the Advertiser or their nominated agent, not ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair.
<br/><br/>
Any Personal Information retained by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair as part of your application will only be used in accord with this Privacy Statement. The use of your information (personal or otherwise) by Advertisers is not within the control of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and if you have any questions about how an Advertiser uses your personal information or want to request access to any personal information that you have sent as part of an application or that has been provided to them as part of a ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile (as defined below), you have the right to contact that Advertiser directly.
<br/><br/>
<strong>ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair provides all Registered Users with the option of creating a personal ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile (“ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile“). A ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile can include a resume, employment and educational history, contact details, salary expectations, and preferred job classifications and locations. Advertisers who are approved by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair are able to search ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile database to find and contact relevant candidates.
<br/><br/>
Advertisers who use the invitations to apply for jobs function will only receive access to your contact information if you respond directly to the job invitation sent to you.
<br/><br/>
If you have replied to a job invitation sent by an Advertiser or you have applied for jobs directly on the Site using your profile, that Advertiser will have access to your up-to-date profile, including your contact details (as updated by you from time to time).
<br/><br/>
All information provided when creating a ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile (including your name, resume, email address, telephone numbers, employment and educational history) may be used by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair for the purpose of improving placement opportunities for you or for tailoring specific products to you.
<br/><br/>
Where you create a ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile on ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair, you consent to your profile being viewed and/or accessed by Advertisers using the websites of any member of the ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Group, which may result in the transfer of your personal data from Singapore to the other countries in which the other members of the ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Group operate.
<br/><br/>
As a Registered User, you can modify your ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile, your resume or modify the privacy options in relation to your ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile at any time, by going to the Profile area of the Site.
<br/><br/>
You may also elect to clear your ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile altogether. Cleared ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profiles may still however be stored by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair in testing or backup systems for a period of time. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair reserves the right to disable or clear a ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile at any time at its sole discretion.
<br/><br/>
Advertisers that place job ads on ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair, and that purchase ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profiles are asked by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair to comply with all relevant laws and obligations relating to the use and disclosure of personal information. The use of your information (personal or otherwise) by these Advertisers is not within the control of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and we cannot accept responsibility for the conduct of these companies.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Storing Your Resume</strong><br/><br/>
You may elect to store resumes in your ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair account, and use those resumes when applying for a job.
<br/><br/>
In order to provide Advertisers with the most relevant information about you, social network information (including but not limited to GitHub or LinkedIn profiles) that you provide may also be scanned by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and relevant content may be displayed to Advertisers. If you do not want content from social networks to be displayed to Advertisers, do not provide social network information.. For more information on how your resume will be used, see above under the heading “ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair Profile”.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Access to or Request for Correction of Data</strong><br/><br/>
You are entitled to request access to or make amendments to your own personal information and data kept with ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair by contacting ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair using the contact details set out under the section headed “Enquiries“. Subject to the paragraph below, you may alternatively edit, amend or delete your personal information and data at any time by logging into the “My Profile” section of the Site.
<br/><br/>
In the event that you wish to access or amend your personal information and data, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair may request you to provide personal details in order to verify your identity.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will respond to your request as soon as reasonably possible. Should ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair not be able to respond to your request within thirty (30) days after receiving your request, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will inform you in writing within thirty (30) days of the time by which ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will be able to respond to your request. Where legally permitted, if ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair is unable to provide you with any personal data or to make a correction requested by you, we shall generally inform you of the reasons why we are unable to do so.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Cookies and Log Files</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair does not collect any personally identifiable information from you while you visit and browse the Site. When you access the Site, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair records your visits only and does not collect your personal information or data. The Site’s server software will also record the domain name, server, address and track the pages you visit and store such information in “cookies”, and gather and store information such as internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, referring/exit pages, operating system, date/time stamp, and clickstream data in log files. All these are done without you being aware that they are occurring.
<br/><br/>
You can choose to accept or decline cookies. Most web browsers automatically accept cookies, but you can modify their individual browser settings to decline cookies if they prefer. However, you should note that disabling cookies on their browser may prevent them from taking full advantage of the Site.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair does not link the information and data automatically collected in the above manner to any personally identifiable information. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair generally uses such automatically collected information and data to estimate the audience size of the Site, gauge the popularity of various parts of the Site, track your movements and number of entries in ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair’ promotional activities and special events, measure traffic patterns and administer the Site. Such automatically collected information and data will not be disclosed save and except in accordance with the section headed “Disclosure or Transfer of Data“.
<br/><br/>
In addition, our third party advertising companies may place cookies on some of the pages you visit on the Site. These cookies are designed to collect non-personally identifiable information in order to analyze your interests and searches on our Site to help deliver more relevant advertisements when you visit our Site. The non-personally identifiable information collected by these cookies may be shared with other third parties for the purpose of managing and targeting advertisements and for market research analysis.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Links to Other Websites</strong><br/><br/>
The Site may provide links to other websites which are not owned or controlled by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair or its affiliates. Personal information and data from you may be collected on these other websites when you visit such websites and make use of the services provided therein. Where and when you decide to click on any advertisement or hyperlink on the Site which grants you access to another website, the protection of your personal information and data which are deemed to be private and confidential may be exposed in these other websites.
<br/><br/>
If you register on the Site via your accounts from social networking sites (including but not limited to Facebook, Google and LinkedIn), you are deemed to have consented to the terms of this Privacy Statement, and such your personal data provided to those networking tools may be obtained by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and be used by ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and its authorized persons in and outside of the your country for the purpose of providing services and marketing materials to the you. Where this occurs, you will be provided clear notice by these social networking sites. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair and its authorized personnel may gain access and use your personal data obtained in such a way, subject to the other provisions of this Privacy Statement.
<br/><br/>
This Privacy Statement is only applicable to the Site. You are reminded that this Privacy Statement grants no protection to your personal information and data that may be exposed on websites other than the Site, and ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair is not responsible for the privacy practices of such other websites. You are strongly recommended to refer to the privacy policies of such other websites before using those websites.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Testimonials</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair posts Users’ testimonials on the Site, which may contain personally identifiable information such as the Users’ names. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair does obtain the Users’ consent prior to posting the testimonials to post their names along with their testimonials.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Security</strong><br/><br/>
The security of your personal information and data is important to ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will always strive to ensure that your personal information and data will be protected against unauthorized access. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair has implemented appropriate electronic and managerial measures in order to safeguard, protect and secure your personal information and data.
<br/><br/>
All personal information and data provided by you are only accessible by the authorized personnel of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair or its authorized third parties, and such personnel shall be instructed to observe the terms of this Privacy Statement when accessing such personal information and data. You may rest assured that their personal information and data will only be kept for as long as is necessary to fulfill the purpose for which it is collected. You should safeguard your unique Username and Password by keeping it secret and confidential and never share these details with anyone.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair uses a third party service provider to facilitate the electronic payment transactions on the Site.
<br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair follows generally accepted industry standards to protect the personal information and data submitted by you to the Site, both during transmission and once ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair receives it. However, no method of transmission over the Internet, or method of electronic storage, is 100% secure. Therefore, while ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair strives to protect your personal information and data against unauthorized access, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair cannot guarantee its absolute security.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Retention of Personal Data</strong><br/><br/>
Once ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair has obtained your personal information and/or data, it will be maintained securely in ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair’ system for the period necessary to fulfill the purposes for which the data was collected as set out under the section headed “Purpose of Collection of Personal Data”. Once registered, you may terminate your membership of the Site by contacting ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair using the contact details under the section headed “Enquiries”. ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair may retain your personal information even after you have closed your account if retention is reasonably necessary to comply with our legal obligations, meet regulatory requirements, resolve disputes between Users, prevent fraud and abuse, or enforce this Privacy Statement and the Terms and Conditions.
<br/><br/>
<strong>Changes in this Privacy Statement</strong><br/><br/>
ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair reserves the right to update, revise, modify or amend this Privacy Statement at any time as ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair deems necessary, so you are strongly recommended to review this Privacy Statement frequently. If ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair decides to update, revise, modify or amend this Privacy Statement, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will post those changes to this webpage and/or other places as ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair deems appropriate, so that you would be aware of what information ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair collects, how ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair uses it, and under what circumstances, if any, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair discloses it.
<br/><br/>
If ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair makes material changes to this Privacy Statement, ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair will notify you on this webpage, by email, or by means of a notice on the home page of ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair.
<br/><br/>
Such changes to this Privacy Statement shall apply from the time that ICON Virtual Internship And Job Fair posts the same on this webpage. Your continued use of the Site and services on the Site shall constitute acceptance of the changes to this Privacy Statement.
<br/><br/>
